<template>
   <vue-tree-nav
    :left="left"
    :right="right"
  ></vue-tree-nav>
</template>

<script>
 import treeNav from 'vue-tree-nav'
export default {
components: {
      treeNav
    },
    data: {
      left: [
        {
          label: 'Home',
          icon: 'home',
          href: '#/home'
        }, {
          label: 'Animals',
          children: [
            {
              label: 'Elephant',
              href: '#/animals/elephant'
            }, {
              label: 'Lion',
              href: '#/animals/lion'
            }, {
              label: 'Bear',
              href: '#/animals/bear'
            }, {
              label: 'Eagle',
              href: '#/animals/eagle'
            }, {
              label: 'Wolf',
              href: '#/animals/wolf'
            }
 
          ]
        }
      ],
      right: [
        {
          href: 'https://github.com/marcodpt/vue-tree-nav',
          icon: 'brands/github'
        }
      ]
    }
}
</script>

<style>

</style>
